{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524300/extras/Husk.gif?t=1730349105\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Journey into a dark-psychedelic shifting realm where nothing is quite as it seems. Delve deep into the shifting Labyrinths of the Archetypes and confront what it truly means to heal.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In EXIT VEIL, players are cast in the role of Tori, a lost soul navigating her way through a beautiful and terrible world on the brink of decay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You\u2019ll collect tarot cards and use them in tense MMO healer class-inspired turn-based battles, where you are always moments away from oblivion. Forever on the back foot you\u2019ll have to test your resolve to snatch victory from the jaws of certain defeat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524300/extras/Clockwork-Nuit.gif?t=1730349105\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lured into the realm by a cryptic plea from a long-lost family member, Tori finds herself caught in a world where the ethereal and mundane intersect. A world dominated by Archetypes, Egregores, Servitors, Daemons, Angels, and The Machine-Elves. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Faced with a malignant source of decay deep within the Labyrinthine Realms, can Tori restore harmony and heal the realms? Or will she remain lost forever, doomed to wander the labyrinth? The choice is yours to make.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Tarot:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tarot sits at the heart of EXIT VEIL. Delve into the EXIT VEIL tarot deck as you progress, cultivating insights that extend beyond the game and into your personal self-discovery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https: